## 8. Pricing y Límites

| API | Costo (por 1,000 requests) | Límite |
|-----|---------------------------|--------|
| Street View Static API | $7.00 USD | 30,000/min |
| JS API Street View | $7.00 USD | Sin límite fijo |
| Street View Tiles | $7.00 USD por 1,000 tiles | Quota diaria |
| Street View Metadata | Gratis | Sin límite |
| Street View Publish | Gratis | Rate limits |

**Free tier**: $200 USD/mes de crédito gratuito de Google Maps Platform.
Equivale a ~28,500 requests de Street View Static gratis al mes.
